SELECT material_name, material_density, analysis_name FROM building_materials JOIN structural_analysis ON building_materials.material_id = structural_analysis.material_id WHERE material_density BETWEEN 70 AND 120;

SELECT DISTINCT material_id, material_name FROM building_materials LEFT JOIN structural_analysis ON building_materials.material_id = structural_analysis.material_id WHERE structural_analysis.material_id IS NULL;

SELECT material_name, COUNT(analysis_id) AS analysis_count FROM building_materials JOIN structural_analysis ON building_materials.material_id = structural_analysis.material_id GROUP BY material_id HAVING COUNT(analysis_id) >= 2 ORDER BY analysis_count DESC;

SELECT m.material_name, p.property_name, s.analysis_date FROM building_materials m JOIN material_properties p ON m.material_id = p.material_id JOIN structural_analysis s ON m.material_id = s.material_id WHERE p.property_value = 'low' ORDER BY s.analysis_date ASC;

SELECT m.material_name, COUNT(s.analysis_id) AS analysis_count FROM building_materials m LEFT JOIN structural_analysis s ON m.material_id = s.material_id GROUP BY m.material_id HAVING analysis_count > 2;
